	<h1 class="title">星巴克CEO写了一封公开信，呼吁15 万美国员工去投票</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
